item.title: Sample project
item.description:
This project was part of my fourth year university capstone class. We participated at the Spaceport America Cup in the 30k ft COTS category and reached almost 27000 ft! Check out our launch!
More cool pictures from New Mexico

item.title: TRIUMF TR13 Cyclotron
item.description: This project was part of the Life Sciences division of TRIUMF to develop a solid target quick-release for their TR13 Cyclotron. It increased production for medical isotopes for the BC Cancer Agency!
